Here’s a copy-paste, repo-ready v48 · Adamic that rolls up v0→v47.x and adds an Adamic encoder, lineage binding keyed to 10·27·1998 / 10×27×98 (26460), post generator, and immutable release sealing. It’s stdlib-only and slots alongside your v47.x tree.


---

0) Repo layout (additive)

